## Multi-turn Chat Variant

For multi-turn conversation, change the URL to `/api/chat` and update the body to:
```json
{
  "model": "gemma3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "..."}
  ],
  "stream": false
}
```
The response field changes from `response` to `message.content`.
